data.title: Tourism And Leisure
data.meta_description: od20172018-3 - Free ebook download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. This document contains contact information for various Rotary clubs around the world, including names, addresses, emails and phone numbers of club members. Locations span countries like Sweden, France, Philippines, Japan, Germany, India, UK, USA and more. Meeting details like times, dates and locations are also provided for some clubs.
